## 1. Create RDDs

```python
rdd1 = sc.parallelize([1,2,3,4,5])
rdd2 = sc.textFile("sample.txt")
rdd3 = rdd1.map(lambda x: x*2)
```

---

## 2. Word Count

```python
rdd = sc.textFile("sample.txt")
word_count = rdd.flatMap(lambda line: line.split()).count()
```

---

## 3. Word Frequency

```python
freq = rdd.flatMap(lambda line: line.split()) \
          .map(lambda word: (word,1)) \
          .reduceByKey(lambda a,b: a+b)
```

---

## 4. Uppercase

```python
upper = rdd.flatMap(lambda line: line.split()) \
           .map(lambda word: word.upper())
```

---

## 5. Lowercase

```python
lower = rdd.flatMap(lambda line: line.split()) \
           .map(lambda word: word.lower())
```

---

## 6. Capitalize

```python
cap = rdd.flatMap(lambda line: line.split()) \
         .map(lambda word: word.capitalize())
```

---

## 7. Word Occurrence

```python
word = "good"
count = rdd.flatMap(lambda line: line.split()) \
           .filter(lambda w: w == word) \
           .count()
```

---

## 8. Filter Sentences

```python
sentences = rdd.filter(lambda line: "good" in line)
```

---

## 9. Longest Word

```python
longest = rdd.flatMap(lambda line: line.split()) \
             .map(lambda word: len(word)) \
             .max()
```

