## 10. Registration → Branch Mapping

```python
def branch_mapper(reg):
    if reg.startswith("58"): return (reg,"BDA")
    elif reg.startswith("57"): return (reg,"AIML")
    elif reg.startswith("38"): return (reg,"VLSI")
    elif reg.startswith("39"): return (reg,"ES")
    elif reg.startswith("47"): return (reg,"CDC")

mapped = reg_rdd.map(branch_mapper)
```

